  "number": 1197,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/1197",
  "title": "fix(toggle) make autoHide check facetValue.count",
  "body": "Activating a toggle with 0 hits puts the user in a state where they can't get back to the previous state.  The toggle and many other widgets autoHide when no results are found.  This change will autoHide the toggle if changing it's state would result in 0 hits.\n\nIssue #1185\n",
